title: Ebro In The Morning - Trash Fathers Day Gifts + Actor/Artist Anthony Ramos
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 6/21.

The Philadelphia 76ers played themselves (11:00), Laura Stylez has her patented Flashing Lights segments (9:00, & 1:15), callers discuss their Trash Fathers Day and Rapper / Actor / Brooklyn's finest - Anthony Ramos joins the Crew (43:00 + 1:17:34). The Crew gives away Summer Jam Tickets and talks Father's Day.

Please like and subscribe to Ebro In The Morning.
